    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a superior blend of performance and sophisticated styling. This unit has been subjected to a comprehensive mechanical evaluation, ensuring that all primary systems operate with precision and reliability. The exterior retains a commendable finish, while the interior remains refined and free of significant wear, indicative of responsible previous ownership. For the professional seeking a dependable and prestigious driving experience without the premium of a showroom-new price point, this vehicle stands as a distinguished choice.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
