      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-loved. It\u2019s perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. I've taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles on the road. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The valvetrain has been meticulously maintained with a recent shim-and-bucket valve adjustment and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis has received critical subframe reinforcement to manage the torque loads of the mechanical limited-slip differential. Performance is further bolstered by refreshed suspension bushings and a dual-mass flywheel that retains factory-spec rotational inertia. While showing minor aesthetic patina, the mechanical synchronization of the individual throttle bodies and the linear power delivery to the 8,000 RPM redline remain sharp and evocative.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used sedan. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Test drives welcome.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i in a classic Alpine White finish. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in impressive aesthetic and mechanical shape. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you may find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014standard signs of careful road use. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather interior is exceptionally clean; the seats show minimal bolster wear, and the cabin is free of any smoke or pet odors. All technological features, including the navigation system, Harman Kardon surround sound, and the panoramic moonroof, are fully operational. Mechanically, this X5 is solid. It features a complete service history with recent work including a new set of spark plugs and a fresh oil service. The Continental tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a turnkey luxury SUV that balances performance with family-friendly utility.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that perfectly embodies the intersection of reliability and performance. This specimen has been meticulously maintained to an exacting standard, ensuring a driving experience that meets the rigorous expectations of the discerning motorist. With a clean aesthetic profile and robust mechanical integrity, this offering represents an exceptional value for those seeking a premium automotive investment. We invite you to evaluate the superior caliber of this automobile firsthand.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
